Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.96,0:21:59.50,ed-jap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be20}Fly high, make it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.67,0:22:02.84,ed-jap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be20}Get to the new world that I seek
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.17,0:22:09.39,ed-jap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be20}Someday, with my little wings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.97,0:22:15.56,ed-jap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be20}Don't look back to the sorrow I left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.98,0:22:21.81,ed-jap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be20}Here's my real intention I hide
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.44,0:22:28.49,ed-jap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be20}I wish you were here, and so just right by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.86,0:22:35.12,ed-jap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be20}Need to be strong enough to swallow my pride
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.33,0:22:40.83,ed-jap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be20}I have been looking for my own style
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.08,0:22:48.38,ed-jap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be20}Don't give it up, here comes the life
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.30,0:22:53.93,ed-jap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be20}Be alive, take it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.01,0:22:57.18,ed-jap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be20}Promise to find, yes I will
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.56,0:23:03.73,ed-jap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be20}Shining wings filled with wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.07,0:23:06.69,ed-jap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be20}Fly high, make it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.73,0:23:10.03,ed-jap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be20}Get to the new world that I seek
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.36,0:23:16.95,ed-jap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be20}Someday, so I believe
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.96,0:21:59.50,ed-chs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be20}{\4a&H80}振翅高飞 翱翔九天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.67,0:22:02.84,ed-chs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be20}{\4a&H80}我将去往自己所追寻的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.17,0:22:09.39,ed-chs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be20}{\4a&H80}终有一日 凭借自己那小小的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.97,0:22:15.56,ed-chs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be20}{\4a&H80}莫回首 将悲伤留在身后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.98,0:22:21.81,ed-chs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be20}{\4a&H80}这才是我的真意所在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.44,0:22:28.49,ed-chs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be20}{\4a&H80}愿君伴我身侧 与我肩并肩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.86,0:22:35.12,ed-chs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be20}{\4a&H80}坚强地包容我的自傲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.33,0:22:40.83,ed-chs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be20}{\4a&H80}我一直在为自己的风格而上下求索
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.08,0:22:48.38,ed-chs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be20}{\4a&H80}莫轻言弃 这才是生命的真义所在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.30,0:22:53.93,ed-chs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be20}{\4a&H80}活下去 莫放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.01,0:22:57.18,ed-chs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be20}{\4a&H80}我坚信 自己必会得到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.56,0:23:03.73,ed-chs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be20}{\4a&H80}那满怀希望 熠熠生辉的双翼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.07,0:23:06.69,ed-chs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be20}{\4a&H80}振翅高飞 翱翔九天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.73,0:23:10.03,ed-chs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be20}{\4a&H80}我将去往自己所追寻的世界
